room_title: Escape room "Under Pressure" by Escapology Mentor in Cleveland
review: My girlfriends and I had our first escape room experience at Escapology and since then, have done several escape rooms over the past few years. We unanimously agree that Escapology has a very high class of escape room that is really hard to match. The technology and the details and quality of workmanship of the clues, traps, and equipment is top notch. Under pressure is very cool!!
